# Feature Architecture

```
features/<name>/
  api/          # schemas, api Effects, query keys, queries
  atoms/        # Effect Atom UI state
  components/   # feature UI
  hooks/        # orchestration hooks
  index.ts      # public API
```

- `*.schema.ts` — Effect Schema; export types via `typeof Schema.Type`.
- `*.query-keys.ts` — query key factory with `as const`.
- `*.queries.ts` — `queryOptions()` + hooks; `queryFn` uses `runApiPromise`.
- `*.atom.ts` — UI atoms with `@effect-atom/atom-react` (not for URL/search state).
- Do not import another feature's internals; use its `index.ts` or shared `@lib`.
